title: Spartacus
description: The life of Spartacus, the gladiator who led a rebellion against the Romans. From his time as an ally of the Romans, to his betrayal and becoming a gladiator, to the rebellion he leads and its ultimate outcome.

title: Justified
description: Enforcing his own brand of justice, U.S. Marshal Raylan Givens, a strong-willed, quiet law-man haunted by his past, returns to his native town to see that justice is served to those in need.

title: Adventure Time
description: A 12-year-old boy and his best friend, a wise 28-year-old dog with magical powers, go on a series of surreal adventures in a remote future.

title: The Pacific
description: The Pacific Theatre of World War II, as seen through the eyes of several young Marines.

title: Strike Back
description: Follows the actions of Section 20, a secretive unit of British military intelligence. A team of special operations personnel conduct several high risk missions across the globe.

title: Rookie Blue
description: Andy McNally and her friends are out of the academy and must adjust to the challenging life of a police officer at the 15th Division in Toronto.

title: Ben 10: Ultimate Alien
description: With his secret identity now revealed to the world, Ben Tennyson continues to fight evil as a superhero with the help of the newly acquired Ultimatrix.

title: Human Target
description: A unique bodyguard protects his clients by secretly infiltrating their lives in order to draw out and eliminate threats.

title: Generator Rex
description: In a future where humans are infected by untested, microscopic robots, a young man with the ability to control the bots helps a government agency control the tech's vicious creations.

title: Millennium
description: The adventures of journalist Mikael Blomkvist and hacker Lisbeth Salander.

title: Angel Beats!
description: Rebellious teens fight in armed combat against one dispassionate girl's supernatural powers in an afterlife high school.

title: The Good Guys
description: Jack is a by-the-book detective whose habit of undermining himself has resulted in a dead-end position with the Police Dept. His partner Dan, a drunken, lecherous veteran hangs onto his job only because of one heroic act years ago.

title: The Slave Hunters
description: Dae-gil is the leader of a group of slave hunters that are hired to find a runaway slave named Tae-ha, who was once a great warrior.

title: The Qwaser of Stigmata
description: Two sisters unwittingly assist a wounded fighter caught in a factional war. He requires sustenance from a female partner to manifest powers, involving the siblings in a conflict where humanity's fate hangs in the balance.

title: Ben Hur
description: A young Jewish prince seeks revenge after an old friend wrongly imprisons him and his family.

title: WWE NXT
description: Wrestlers will portray heroes or villains as they follow a series of events that build tension and culminate in a wrestling match or series of matches.

title: Dreamworks How to Train Your Dragon Legends
description: In this set of shorts Hiccup and the gang learn about different species of dragons.Then, Gobber goes in search of the Boneknapper Dragon.

title: Demon King Daimao
description: Demon King Daimao follows Akuto Sai as the lead character, who on the day he enters Constant Magic Academy, receives a very unexpected future occupation aptitude test result: "Devil King."

title: Kick Buttowski: Suburban Daredevil
description: A satirical look at a 10-year-old boy who aspires to be the most hardcore daredevil in existence.

title: Arn
description: Arn must endure a great ordeal before he can get the love of his life Cecile, who has been confined to a monastery.

title: Black Lagoon: Roberta's Blood Trail
description: The 'bloodhound' awakens when her master, and head of the Lovelace family is assassinated.

title: El cartel 2 - La guerra total
description: Now Pepe Cadena finishes telling the story in which the most powerful drug traffickers in Colombia are strengthened but later fall while he and others dedicate themselves to the dangerous task of exposing them to collaborate with justice.

title: Badass!
description: The world's favorite Supermodels are chosen to attempt dangerous daring extreme sports and excursions like never before.

title: Unnatural History
description: A young man is sent to live with his uncle and cousin in Washington DC by his anthropologist parents. In the process, he must use the skills he learned around the world in order to solve various crimes and conspiracies.

title: Black Panther
description: Black Panther is the ruler and protector of the African nation of Wakanda. Using technology, wits, and extraordinary fighting ability he must protect his nation from an invasion led by Ulysses Klaw, the man who killed his father.

title: Dance in the Vampire Bund
description: Vampire queen Mina Tepes comes out of hiding to offer peace between vampires and humans. Japan gives her a bund, where she goes to live with her people. However, extremist human and vampire groups do not want to coexist.

title: Mobile Suit Gundam Unicorn
description: A conspiracy around Laplace's Box is potentially going to start another war between the Earth Federation and Neo Zeon. Chosen by fate, Banagher Links gets the key to the box, and must follow his heart to decide what to do with it.

title: Nura: Rise of the Yokai Clan
description: Rikuo Nura appears to be an average middle school student. No one knows that he comes home every day to a house full of youkai, nor that he transforms into the all-powerful leader of these spirits at night. However, much to the disappointment of many, Rikuo is determined to live as normal a life as possible.

title: A Man Called God
description: After his parents' murder, Michael King, a drug lord, seeks revenge on those responsible. But his ruthless pursuit is challenged when he falls for Jin Bo Bae, a journalist.

title: Giant
description: This drama tells the story of three siblings who grew up in the 1970's. Lee Kang Mo, his older brother Sung Mo and younger sister Mi Joo were separated at a young age when their father was killed in a smuggling scheme and their mother also died subsequently. When they are able to reunite years later, they had all reached adulthood and are determined to exact revenge upon the people responsible for their misery.

title: Miami Medical
description: A medical drama about a team of expert trauma surgeons, who shine brightest when working under pressure against the clock to save critically injured patients.

title: Katanagatari
description: Kyotoryuu, is the legendary fencing school. Instead of a sword, however, the hands and legs are used as weapons.

title: Ihanet
description: A assassination occurred in one of Turkey's largest conglomerates. A young policeman whose assassinated ending sister is murdered enters into a great struggle to get his sister's revenge. One dimension of this struggle is the holding and international business relations.

title: Hakuouki
description: When her father has disappeared, Chizuru Yukimura goes searching for him in Kyoto. She is attacked by strange men, and then rescued by the Shinsengumi.

title: Darker Than Black: Gaiden
description: Tells the story of what happened to Yin and Hei between the first and second instalments.
originalTitle: Darker Than Black - Kuro no Kieyakusha: Gaiden

title: Bakugan Battle Brawlers: Gundalian Invaders
description: Follows human battle brawlers who wield creatures called Bakugan in a parallel-dimension battle that shifts into our world.

title: Tensou Sentai Goseiger
description: Unknown to the people of Earth, there is a branch of humanity called the Gosei Angels whose mission is to protect the Earth. When the Earth is targeted by an evil alien invasion force called Warstar, they destroy the Heaven's Tower, the bridge between the Earth and the Gosei World, home of the Gosei Angels, to keep them from interfering. Five apprentice Gosei Angels use their powers to defend the earth as the Goseigers

title: Missing
description: The Altamira family celebrate Mariuno's birthday. Elisa and her cousins ask for permission to go dancing at a new club in town.

title: Ask ve Ceza
description: When Yasemin, who gave her virginity to a stranger, gets pregnant and realizes that the baby is the heir of a dangerous rich tribe, she gets scared and hides the baby. But she meets the baby's father again.

title: HeartCatch PreCure!
description: Tsubomi Hanasaki is determined to become more outgoing. Upon becoming a PreCure, she is ecstatic - until her shyness proves an obstacle. However, with her new friend Erika, she is determined to eventually become a stronger person.

title: Violette1st's Raging Series
description: The Series is Based on Angry Grandpa, and Psycho Series, involving about a young William Anderson Jr. and Violette Needs to control him to get calm and William Always on his Xbox.

title: Zacatillo, un lugar en tu corazón
description: Miriam, given her ambition, has decided to kill Karla and keep her money, however, she saves herself from the attack and to hide and avoid being discovered she changes her name.

title: Majisuka gakuen
description: A teenage transfer student enrolls at an all-girls high school. Upon defending a fellow student during a schoolyard fight, her martial arts skills are revealed, and soon she must fight a series of fearsome opponents, each one tougher than the one before.

title: Iron Man: Extremis
description: An experimental serum called Extremis gets stolen, and Iron Man rockets into action. The ensuing battles test Stark's spirit and Iron Man's power. Based on the graphic novel of the same name.

title: Journey to the West
description: A new version of the Journey to the West. The series features a scenic setting across China as it follows the Monk and his disciples on their quest for the scriptures and towards enlightenment.

title: Hero 108
description: Big Green, a peacekeeping force of superhumans and animals, work to establish peace between the kingdoms of humans and animals.

title: Heroman
description: One day Joey rescues and fixes a broken toy robot. Joey allows it be in his room. One stormy evening, the toy is hit by a lightning bolt, it gives it life and a reason to exist. To fight for Joey and the dangerous ordeals that shall come.

title: The League of S.T.E.A.M.
description: The League of S.T.E.A.M. (Supernatural and Troublesome Ectoplasmic Apparition Management) is an organization comprised of Inventors, Scientists, Adventurers, Craftsmen, Monster and Creature Hunters, and Paranormal Researchers.

title: Jonah Hex: Motion Comics
description: One long and two short motion comic adventures of Jonah Hex, a deadly cynical bounty hunter with a lip and a horrible facial scar. He hunts a necromancer and his crony - undead Wild Bill Hickok, some robbers and a rotten old judge.

title: Trenches
description: Locked in a grueling war on a remote planet, two enemies find themselves abandoned by their own. They must put aside their differences and work together if they are to survive. And they better do it quick - they are not alone on this rock.

title: The Blockbuster Buster
description: A fan-boy of almost every popular franchise review the movies that ruined them, such as failed prequels, adaptions, and remakes, using his magic hammer.

title: The Dukes of Bröxstônia
description: The Dukes are the hottest band to come out of Bröxstônia. Thanks to the generosity of the Bröxstônian government, The Dukes are on tour, spreading their uniquely punk thrash sounds to an unsuspecting world.

title: Io e mio figlio - Nuove storie per il commissario Vivaldi
description: In Italian with English subtitles. Inspector Federico Vivaldi is an old-school cop in a new world: his son is gay, his wife has left him and an ambitious colleague is angling to take over his position. He may be old-fashioned, but he's resilient enough to find his way in his new reality.

title: Black Intelligence
description: Major Ahmadi is the Deputy Director of the Anti-Corruption Prevention and Combating Computer Crime Center, who has been involved with the complex case of a dengerous killer and a genius hacker named Jamshid Kazemi ,also known as Kamran bouryaei.

title: This Movie Sucks!
description: Ed The Sock invites friends over to view really bad movies, and then make fun of them.

title: Sumo Mouse
description: When Yama's uncle is kidnapped by the most powerful cat in Catropolis, he vows to find him. What he finds instead is his destiny, in an ancient o-icho, a sumo top knot, which when worn, transforms Yama into Sumo Mouse.

title: Transformers: Cyber Missions
description: An animated series by TG Studios set after Revenge of the Fallen.

title: Death Game Park
description: "Death Game Park" is an action thriller reminiscent of Kinji Fukasaku's "Battle Royale." A group of young adults have been forced to participate in a "death game" for an unknown purpose. Unable to call for help, they have to muster their strength in order to survive and find a way to escape. Note: This is a Mobile Drama (BeeTV) and has around 24 episodes with the episodes being around 5 minutes each. However, the subbers (TV-Nihon) have merged this all into one long "movie."

title: Feroz
description: When the Cruz family returns to his hometown are victims of strange events related to the werewolf.

title: CSI: SFP
description: CSI SFP, takes place in Santa Fe at the made up school of Pendon Academy. It follows young bright officers as they solve cases and help rid the high school of crime, and move up the ladder from officer to maybe even captain, these are their stories.

title: Gumapang ka sa lusak
description: Gumapang Ka sa Lusak revolves around the lives of engaged sweethearts Rachel (Jennylyn Mercado), an aspiring young actress, and Levi (Dennis Trillo), a poor, happy-go-lucky guy. In the town of San Felipe, Rachel's beauty stands out. She becomes the object of desire for many men, including their Mayor, Edmundo Guatlo (Al Tantay). With a fervent desire to have her, Mayor Guatlo will use all his power to make Rachel his mistress. Rachel rejects all the gifts and favors he offers her, but she falls into the wicked mayor's trap after a series of misfortunes happens to her loved ones, including her fiancé Levi, who gets imprisoned for to an illegal activity. Although the mayor's wife Rowena (Sandy Andolong) is aware of her husband's infidelity, she goes along with it as long as the affair doesn't affect her comfortable, powerful position in society. Then the mayor's secret is exposed to the public, a secret that uncovers a series of other secrets. Will the mayor be able to win again in the upcoming election? Will the expose' free Rachel from being the Mayor's mistress? Will fate lead her back to Levi's loving arms? Or is it too late for the hapless lovers to rekindle their affection?

title: Night Raid 1931
description: In Shanghai, in 1931, the seeds of future devastating war are being planted by various factions. Sakurai Kikan, a secret agency whose agents have paranormal abilities, must uncover their plans and stop them before it's too late.

title: Okamikakushi ~ Masque of the Wolf
description: Kuzumi Hiroshi moves to the town of Joga with his father and his handicapped sister. The town's stories of man-like wolves seem like small town lore. But when people start to go missing, it's not out of the realm of possibility.

title: Panday Kids
description: Three kids destined to protect the world from the evil Lizardo using the shards of the Panday Sword. Oliver is the Heart (Puso) of the team, Hadji is the Bravery (Tapang), and Charlie is the Intelligence (Talino).

title: Tonyong bayawak
description: Antonio "Tonyo" Dela Cruz (Coco Martin), a responsible father who hunts monitor lizards for a living has been chosen by a fairy of the forest to battle injustice and to restore peace in Cavite under the guise of Tonyong Bayawak. But the death of his wife Maring leads him to cross the thin line between hero and vigilante.

title: Lucha Libre USA: Masked Warriors
description: Lucha Libre USA: Masked Warriors, the high-spirited Mexican style wrestling that marries exciting aerial maneuvers and extraordinary acrobatics with the greatest Lucha-stars from Mexico and the best in American pro wrestling.

title: Wrestlicious Takedown
description: Wrestlicious TakeDown was the Main Television program produced by Wrestlicious which ran on Dish Network, via MavTV in the United States and BiteTV in Canada,

title: The G.A.M.E.
description: It's been one year since the "Overachievers" series was released, so Jesse decided to host a reunion. All hell breaks loose following the party as aliens arrive on Earth leaving Jesse and Pat to take matters into their own hands. It all comes to a head as they realize they're caught up in something they're powerless to stop, just one big G.A.M.E.

title: Live or Die
description: The residents of Waterman Avenue struggle with friendships, their parents, their health, and their pasts.

title: YouTube Assassin
description: Joe Nation hires mullet-head assassin, 'Bob Thunder', to take down some of YouTube's top creators.

title: Donramon y Perchita
description: Online series about the adventures of DonRamon and Perchita

title: Armored Trooper VOTOMS: Phantom Chapter
description: Gotho takes Vanilla and Coconna, on a tour that they spent with Chirico Cuvie from the original television series, there they meet old friends and relive their old memories.

title: Battle Hero Absolute
description: Inspired by the Japanese Superhero show Kamen Rider, Battle Hero Absolute is about a young man named Jay, who fights a human replicating alien species called the Clarion. Using the only Earth weapon capable of identifying and fighting the stealth menace, he is called upon to be the protector of the human race as the Masked Hero. All while juggling his college studies and his relationships with his girlfriend Jan and his former lover, but lifelong best friend Sunny who also moonlights as the 2nd Battle Hero. Both of whom have a peculiar fascination with the local superhero.

title: Adrenalina
description: Watch these daredevils as they take on exhilarating, albeit unconventional, sports, like cage diving with sharks in Hawaii.

title: Karaté Boy
description: Karaté Boy, the last man on Earth, tries to survive in the ruins of the civilization and looking for other survivors.

title: Cowboy and Lucky
description: Cowboy and Lucky covers the misadventures of two brothers, "Cowboy" and "Lucky," trying their luck as bounty hunters, private investigators or better yet idiots for hire while also babysitting a smart mouth, talent musician runaway "Delia".

title: The Replacement
description: Torian, a retired armed forces black ops specialist with shattered memories, now turned assassin, is trying to escape the nightmares from his past and regain what he lost. His agent Scarlet, working under the disguise of her law firm, finds a way to keep Torian in the game of killing but may ultimately lead him down the tunnel of vengeance and hope he may have been looking for all along.

title: Apollo Z. Hack: A Reviewaverse Saga
Elias Paniki
description: Elias' mother died the night she gave birth to Elias. And so Elias went to live with his foster parents. Elias takes up mixed martial arts: Muay Thai training undertaken by a soldier named Victor, and given an amulet with extraordinary powers, the "bertud ng paniki." He uses the amulet to fight off the mangkukulam who is feared to have returned.

title: Fragment
description: A television series of dramatic-documentary films exploring lesser-known facts and events from Georgian history. This cycle delves into the intriguing and often overlooked aspects of Georgia's past, blending historical analysis with dramatic reenactments to bring forgotten stories to life. Each episode unveils a unique chapter, offering viewers a fresh perspective on the rich and complex history of Georgia.

title: Rise of the Rebellion
description: Set in the Galactic Empire era. Two Rebel spies travel to the Empire-occupied planet Eison, where they meet new allies, alien creatures, and the Empire.

title: Guns for Hire
description: A no-name college student finds himself in the sights of a corrupt politician.

title: NJPW Circuit 2010 New Japan Cup ~ the Perfect Generalist
F22: The Web Series
description: Raised by her grandparents, Nika had been told that her parents died in a car crash when she was five. Now years later, she is given a thumb drive containing some old footage proving that her parents were actually killed by a shadowy government agency. Coming home to a ransacked apartment, she flees, fearing for her life. Thus begins a three-year undercover journey, armed only with her camera and her wits. With clues supplied to her by various unknown sources, Nika hopes to expose the Faceless Government Entity for what it is. Using her camera as a weapon, she adds pieces to the puzzle by posting electronic evidence to the group of agents who have taken up her cause.

title: 30 Seconds from Oblivion
description: Each year, thousands of people flock to Phoenix Arizona to live. And it's no wonder why. Gang activity and drug violence has nearly been wiped out. Crime rate in the city sits at historic lows. For the first time in a long while, people feel safe again. The Chief of police has one man to thank for that. Micheal Warthers. However Micheal is no saint. Quite the opposite. For four years now, he and the chief have quietly worked out a deal. Amnesty for him and his men for bringing in certain kinds of drugs and enforcing a violence free street. As long as the police could tax the money he made, and things were kept quiet, everyone was happy. Now that the city has gotten cleaned up, The police chief wants to revoke control. Micheal has other plans.

title: Danger Coast
description: Danger Coast follows the dramatic exploits of Miami-Dade County's elite waterborne Marine Operations Bureau as they engage in unexpected, life-saving activities that no training or experience could prepare them for.

title: A God Named Pablo
description: The last two sons of Zeus search for the Golden Fleece in modern day LA.

title: NJPW J Sports Crown Openweight Six Man Tag Team Tournament
NJPW Best of the Super Junior XVII ~ Strike Gold
